    dc:description "FIGURE 9. Pirata punctipes (Gravely, 1924) comb. nov., types of Lycosa punctipes Gravely, 1924. A female lectotype habitus, dorsal. B female paralectotype habitus, dorsal. C egg sac of female lectotype. D labels from type tube. Scale bars: A–C, 2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10145911/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10145913>
    dc:description "FIGURE 10. Pirata punctipes (Gravely, 1924) comb. nov., types of Lycosa punctipes Gravely, 1924. A intact epigyne of female lectotype, ventral. B epigyne of female paralectotype cleared in 10% KOH, ventral. C same, dorsal. Scale bars: A–C, 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10145913/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

